BLKASIAA.MX.short_name: BLK Acciones Asia SA de CV S.I
BLKASIAA.MX.long_name: BLK Acciones Asia SA de CV S.I.R.V. A
BLKASIAA.MX.summary: BNMASIA is an investment company that invests primarily (at least 80% of total assets) in shares belonging to the Asian stock market, either directly, through ETFs (Exchange Traded Funds) and / or by purchasing shares national investment companies and / or foreign equities. Stocks and ETFs will be listed in the International Quotation System ("SIC") or quoted on the Mexican Stock Exchange. BNMASIA seek to provide competitive performance with respect to the performance of the MSCI AC Asia ex Japan, less costs and taxes of the respective series.
BLKASIAA.MX.family: Impulsora de Fondos Banamex SA de CV
